title: Sounds of the 70's : Here Comes the Weekend

sources.title: Sounds of the 70's : Here Comes the Weekend
sources.description:
From an era before Spotify wrapped, and even before MTV, This music doco includes newsreels from the headlines from the Seventies, with facts and information about the artists and the songs. Some amazing times and some amazing performances...

See live performances of Blondie, Stealers Wheel, Showaddywaddy, Tavares, Nazareth, Status Quo, Brian Eno & Tubeway Army, Dave Edmunds, Tom Petty, The Specials, Freddy Mercury & Queen, Thin Lizzy, Racey, The Jam, Rod Stewart, and more.

Director: Jason Fenwick
Year 2021
